    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in poor condition. It has significant mechanical issues that will require substantial repair before reliable use. The exterior shows heavy wear, including multiple scratches, dents, and faded paint. The interior is worn and damaged, with noticeable tears, stains, and non-functional features. Best suited for someone willing to invest in repairs or looking for parts.",
